{
  "stem": "27390.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they-- out in the paper, there was a plan where the ghetto was going to be.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And every day, a different street was going to be moved into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the people that lived in the ghetto, the Germans and the Jews, were going to be moved out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this-- according to this plan, they were going to take maybe 18 months or 2 years to transfer a quarter of a million Jews into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And to move out all the other people out of the ghetto, to give them-- to settle them in, it was a long, drawn-out process.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we, you know, being optimists, we thought, oh, the war will be finished by then.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Till they get around to do all these things, it will be all over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So one afternoon, my mother went to the market.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was on a Thursday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remembered like it will be now, although it was 55 years ago, 56 years ago.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1940, it was in March.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- it's near 57 years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother went to the market to buy chicken, meat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could still get what you wanted if you had the money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was scarce, but-- but you could still buy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As she was coming home, she saw a lot of soldiers in our area, German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She didn't take much notice of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She came in, and she told my father this, that there were more soldiers than usual.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as I looked out the window, [PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] [DRINKS] I saw through the window soldiers surrounding the block where we lived.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I told this to my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he didn't dare go to the window in case he was seen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we children, we took a chance.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
